Class SeedSocket

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • request.SeedSocket
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class SeedSocket
extends java.lang.Thread
    This class creates a background thread which connects to a server and downloads a seed data, appending it to the supplied file. There are also calls which allow the calling program to keep track of the status of the download.
